{{distinguish|硫酰胺}}
'''硫代酰胺'''（Thioamide）是[[酰胺|酰胺]]的[[硫代|硫代]][[类似物|类似物]]。通式 R-CS-NR'R"。常见的硫代酰胺如[[硫代乙酰胺|硫代乙酰胺]]（CH<sub>3</sub>C(S)NH<sub>2</sub>）。

==性质==
与酰胺相比，硫代酰胺的 C–N 键重键成分更强，旋转能垒更高。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=Why Does Thioformamide Have a Larger Rotational Barrier Than Formamide? |author=Kenneth B. Wiberg, Paul R. Rablen |journal=J. Am. Chem. Soc. |year=1995 |volume=117 |issue=8 |pages=2201–2209}}</ref>

==制取==
一般由相应酰胺与[[五硫化二磷|五硫化二磷]]或[[劳森试剂|劳森试剂]]反应制备。<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = R. Gompper, W. Elser | title = 2-Methylmercapto-N-Methyl-Δ2-Pyrroline | collvol = 5 | collvolpages = 780 | year = 1973 | prep = CV5P0780}}</ref><ref>{{OrgSynth | author = George Schwarz | title = 2,4-Dimethylthiazole" Organic Syntheses | collvol = 3 | collvolpages = 332 | year = 1955 | prep = CV3P0332}}</ref> 也可由[[腈|腈]]与[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]作用或通过[[Willgerodt-Kindler反应|Willgerodt-Kindler反应]]得到。

==用途==
用作[[有机合成|有机合成]]试剂；另外，也用作治療[[甲状腺功能亢进症|甲状腺功能亢进症]]之藥物。

